---
title: HelloHero: Kiwi Salmon & Roast Pumpkin Toss with Herbed Mayo & Crispy Shallots
description: Who doesn’t like a bit of spice on their salmon? This one gets a generous coating of our punchy Kiwi spice blend before it crisps up in the pan until golden. Finish it off with a bed of roasted veggies (that'll take barely any effort to whip up) and top it off with a sprinkling of crispy shallots for an outstanding pairing of flavours – without the sweat and tears.

